{
  "texts": [
    "It is worth noting that 7 generalized types of soft semi-compact spaces were defined by these authors.Another classical topic in topology is the analysis of separability axioms.",
    "They have motivated Alcantud [47] to construct soft topological spaces that are well-behaved in relation to these ideas.",
    "In addition, two classes of axioms generalizing suitable soft separability ideas were introduced by [60].",
    "Their inspiration was the countable chain condition and the topological concept of caliber.",
    "In their article, the role of cardinality in both the countable chain condition and the finite chain condition is deeply investigated."
  ]
}